text: Kırkpınar is a Turkish oil-wrestling tournament, held annually since 1346. *Kırkpınar, Bayburt, a village in Bayburt Province, Turkey *Kırkpınar, Korkuteli, a village in Antalya Province, Turkey *Kırkpınar, Emirdağ, a village in Afyonkarahisar Province, Turkey
